---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Us - Zcompressor | Developer-Grade Local PDF Compressor"
  description="Discover Zcompressor's story and why we believe in 100% private, client-side document processing."
  ogUrl="https://Zcompressor.com/about"
>
  <Header />

  <main class="min-h-screen bg-canvas-soft text-ink py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto">
      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div class="mb-12 border-b border-hairline pb-8">
        <span
          class="text-caption-mono font-mono text-link-deep uppercase tracking-wider block mb-3"
        >
          Our Philosophy
        </span>
        <h1
          class="text-display-lg md:text-display-xl text-ink font-semibold tracking-[-1.5px] md:tracking-[-2.4px] mb-4"
        >
          About Zcompressor.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-body-lg text-body">
          We built Zcompressor to solve a fundamental security flaw in online
          utility tools: the requirement to upload personal documents to remote
          servers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <article class="space-y-10">
        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-display-md text-ink font-semibold tracking-[-0.96px] mb-4"
          >
            The Problem with Web Uploads.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body-md text-body leading-relaxed">
            Most online PDF compressors require you to upload your files to
            their servers. Even if a service claims to "delete files after 1
            hour," your documents are still transmitted over the internet,
            processed on remote infrastructure, and briefly stored on someone
            else's system.
          </p>
          <p class="text-body-md text-body leading-relaxed">
            For developers, businesses, lawyers, and healthcare professionals,
            uploading sensitive records (contracts, medical logs, financial
            audits, API keys, or private databases) to a third-party server
            represents an unacceptable compliance risk.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Feature Grid/List -->
        <section
          class="bg-canvas border border-hairline rounded-lg p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-level-3 space-y-6"
        >
          <h3 class="text-display-sm text-ink font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px]">
            The Zcompressor Difference.
          </h3>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-2">
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h4 class="text-body-md-strong text-ink flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-cyan-deep"></i> 100% Private
              </h4>
              <p class="text-body-sm text-body">
                Processing runs inside a secure local sandbox in your browser.
                Files never touch the cloud.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h4 class="text-body-md-strong text-ink flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt text-warning-deep"></i> No Upload Bottlenecks
              </h4>
              <p class="text-body-sm text-body">
                Local compression skips slow internet uploads. Large files
                process immediately.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h4 class="text-body-md-strong text-ink flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-code text-link-deep"></i> Modern Web APIs
              </h4>
              <p class="text-body-sm text-body">
                Leverages local browser thread workers, canvas APIs, and memory pipelines for fast, client-side operations.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h4 class="text-body-md-strong text-ink flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles text-violet"></i> 100% Free
              </h4>
              <p class="text-body-sm text-body">
                No subscription, no watermarks, no registration, and no file
                limits. Period.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2
            class="text-display-md text-ink font-semibold tracking-[-0.96px] mb-4"
          >
            Under the Hood.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body-md text-body leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Zcompressor leverages cutting-edge web standard technologies to
            execute client-side compression:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-body-md text-body mb-6">
            <li>
              <strong>Astro & Tailwind CSS v4</strong>: A high-performance,
              modern framework stack that renders highly optimized, static,
              responsive HTML markup.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Mozilla PDF.js</strong>: Renders high-quality PDF page
              viewports onto local HTML5 Canvas bitmaps in browser thread
              workers.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>pdf-lib</strong>: Rewrites and downsamples internal PDF
              document objects, stream metadata, and image structures without
              remote APIs.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>JSZip</strong>: Bundles multiple compressed PDFs into a
              single, structured download in memory.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="border-t border-hairline pt-8">
          <h2
            class="text-display-md text-ink font-semibold tracking-[-0.96px] mb-4"
          >
            Our Mission.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body-md text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
            We believe that basic file utilities should be local utility
            operations. Our mission is to continue delivering privacy-first,
            web-native utility tools that respect user data and security.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a
              href="/#compressor"
              class="px-5 h-[40px] bg-primary text-on-primary text-body-sm-strong rounded-pill hover:bg-black transition-colors inline-flex items-center justify-center shadow-level-2 focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary focus-visible:outline-none"
            >
              Start Compressing
            </a>
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="px-5 h-[40px] bg-canvas text-ink border border-hairline text-body-sm-strong rounded-pill hover:bg-canvas-soft transition-colors inline-flex items-center justify-center shadow-level-1 focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary focus-visible:outline-none"
            >
              Contact Our Team
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
